---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, trunc(score, 3) as score FROM vector_search(qs_view, 'secondary', answer) where subject!='math' order by score desc, id LIMIT 4"
snapshot_kind: text
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                                      |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer).score, Int64(3)) AS score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer) projection=[answer, id, score], full_filters=[vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("secondary"), answer).subject != Utf8("math")]                       |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                               |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@2 as answer, trunc(score@1, 3) as score]                                                                                                                           |
|               |       FilterExec: subject@3 != math, projection=[id@0, score@1, answer@2]                                                                                                                                       |
|               |         HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, on=[(id@0, id@1), (question@1, question@2)], projection=[id@0, score@2, answer@3, subject@6]                                                            |
|               |           CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |             ProjectionExec: expr=[union_extract(json_get(key@0, id), int) as id, union_extract(json_get(key@0, question), str) as question, 1 - distance@1 as score]                                            |
|               |               CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                            |
|               |                   BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                       S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=30                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                  |
|               |             FilterExec: subject@3 != math                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                              |
